Conditions in the event of claims:
.sp 3mm
.of 5mm
*¤The cardholder is to inform Forsikringsrådgiverne without undue delay
after noticing the covered function failure, and before the cardholder
proceeds with the repair.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤On confirmation of justification, Forsikringsrådgiverne will inform the
cardholder of either the name or the telephone number of a repair workshop,
or take steps to ensure that the repair workshop phones the policy holder.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤All repairs are to be performed by an authorised repair workshop as
stipulated by Forsikringsrådgiverne.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Functional defects in electrical appliances/white goods that are less
than two years old must always be reported first to the shop from which the
item was purchased. Insured persons resident on Greenland or the Faeroe
Islands have only a one-year right to file complaints pursuant to local
legislation. For this reason, insured persons resident here may only file
claims for goods in the shop where said goods were purchased if the fault
or defect arises within the first year.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The claim report is to include:
.sp 3mm
.of 5mm
*¤Card number.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤A brief description of the claim.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤A copy of the purchase receipt and a copy of the account statement
proving that the card was used to purchase the object/item in question.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤All other documentation or information that is necessary to allow
Forsikringsrådgiverne to process the report and calculate the appropriate
compensation - for example, through obtaining an approximate price for
repairing the item.
