4.0 What does the insurance cover?
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
4.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
4.1.1 The insurance covers functional defects, i.e. 'internal damage'.
.kp off
.kp on
4.1.2 The insurance covers selected
.us
consumer electronics
(Hi-Fi systems, TVs, games consoles, cameras, video cameras,
DVD players, computers, GPS units and the like
(see Article 4.1.3, however) as well as
.us
white goods
(washing machines, tumble dryers, ovens, freezers, refrigerators and so
on) located in Denmark (own residence or holiday home), whose purchase
price exceeds DKK 1,500 (including VAT, but excluding delivery costs) on
condition that the insured paid the full purchase price with his/her
card. For insured persons resident on Greenland or the Faeroe Islands, the
items must be located in their residence there.
.kp off
.kp on
4.1.3 The insurance only covers new items purchased with the
insured's MasterCard
.if &U'X&KTMCPROD = XG
.th Gold card
.el Platinum card
from a VAT-registered or
correspondingly registered dealer in Denmark. For insured persons
resident on Greenland or the Faeroe Islands, purchases made there are
also covered by the insurance. The purchase of items over the
Internet is covered on condition the website is based in Denmark and
subject to the Danish Sale of Goods Act, or based in Greenland or the
Faeroe Islands and subject to the Greenlandic or Faeroese Sale of
Goods Act.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤The insurance provides coverage for a period of up to three years after
the time at which the right to complain to the seller ceases, see Section
83 of the Danish Sale of Goods Act.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤The insurance coverage comes into effect at the time where the policy
holder's right to claim faults/defects against the seller has ceased
pursuant to Section 83 of the Danish Sale of Goods Act (the purchase must
be covered by the Danish Sale of Goods Act or, if the insured is resident
on Greenland or the Faeroe Islands, by the Greenlandic or Faeroese Sale of
Goods Act). For insured persons resident in Denmark, this means at least
two years after the object of the sale has been transferred to the
purchaser, while the deadline for insured persons resident on Greenland or
the Faeroe Islands is one year after said date.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤If the dealer has provided a longer complaints period than the
standard period stated in the Danish Sale of Goods Act - see Section 83
of said Act - the extended complaints deadline shall apply in relation
to this insurance as from the time when the dealer's extended
complaints period terminates, and with a reduced period such that the
total complaints period (the complaints period provided by the dealer
plus the extended complaints period in
accordance with this insurance policy) does not exceed five years.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤If the insured cancels his/her card, items purchased using the card are
still covered according to the present insurance terms and conditions for
up to three years subsequent to the expiry of the original deadline for
filing complaints regarding the item insured.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED
4.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
.of 5mm
*¤The maximum limit for the insurance company's obligations is DKK
50,000 per year, irrespective of the number of claims, and no more than
DKK 25,000 per claim.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤Estimation of the damage is based on the price for replacement.
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤The upper limit per claim is the purchase price of the item insured
as stated on the card receipt, irrespective of whether the cost of
repair or repurchase may be higher. If repair or replacement would be
more costly, compensation will be paid by the insured's MasterCard
being credited with a sum corresponding to the original purchase
price, less the fall in value attributable to the age of the item
(including VAT but excluding transport costs).
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤The insurance company is entitled to decide whether a damaged item is
to be replaced through repair, through cash compensation, or through
the provision of a corresponding new or used item.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The insurance is without excess.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
